    {
      "id": "t32",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.text-align-center > div.max-width-large > p.text-size-medium",
      "en": "At IOI Oleochemical, sustainability is core to our operations. We source certified raw materials from responsible suppliers while maintaining NDPE, RSPO and regulatory compliance. Through transparent tracking and responsible logistics, we deliver ethically sustainable oleochemicals."
    },
    {
      "id": "t33",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.w-layout-grid > div.layout54_content-left > h2.heading-style-h2",
      "en": "Midstream leadership in sustainable oleochemicals"
    },
    {
      "id": "t34",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout54_content-right > div.margin-bottom > p.text-size-medium",
      "en": "IOI Oleochemical sources responsibly because we understand our place in complex supply chains. Our commitment runs deep, backed by IOI Corporation's founding RSPO membership and our own certified operations."
    },
    {
      "id": "t35",
      "type": "text",
